#

Greek Yogurt Guacamole

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyAvocado

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegetarianLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SnackDipEasyHealthy

Description

A creamy blend of avocados and Greek yogurt with a zesty twist, perfect as a dip or spread.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • greek yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • chopped cilantro: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
